    {
        "id": "ec_comment",
        "type": "comment",
        "z": "tab_entity_controller",
        "name": "How to use this flow",
        "info": "Control an entity's state via the Fleet Manager API. Click an inject button to change the 'Gallery Light 1' entity's brightness. The MQTT listener below shows real-time state change events.\n\nPrerequisite: Create an entity with slug 'gallery-light-1' via the Fleet Manager API or Dashboard first.\n\nThe top row sends HTTP POST requests to update entity state.\nThe bottom row listens for MQTT state change notifications that are broadcast when the state updates.",
